text: Vale David Cunningham (19 October 1928 - 20 October 2020) was an Australian ice hockey player. He competed in the men's tournament at the 1960 Winter Olympics. He was born in Brunswick, Victoria. Cunningham died on 20 October 2020, one day after his 92nd birthday.Dave Cunningham's obituary ==References== Category:1928 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Australian ice hockey players Category:Olympians for Australia Category:Sportspeople from Victoria (Australia)
